      <p>Although many times larger, growing to a length of about 5 feet, <a href="ch74s02.html#MonstersVermin7">giant bees</a> behave generally the same as their smaller cousins. <a href="ch74s02.html#MonstersVermin7">Giant bees</a> are usually not aggressive except when defending themselves or their hive.</p>
