        <p><span class="strong"><strong>Poison (Ex):</strong></span> Injury, Fortitude DC 11, initial and secondary damage 1d4 Con. The save DC is Constitution-based. A <a href="ch74s02.html#MonstersVermin7">giant bee</a> that successfully stings another creature pulls away, leaving its stinger in the creature. The bee then dies.</p>
      </div>
